OL,6,FA mother and son have been jailed
OL,7,Fafter a little boy suffered serious
OL,8,Finjuries in a "savage and sustained
OL,9,Fattack" by an XL bully.
OL,11,FThe eight year old victim, who cannot
OL,12,Fbe named, was attacked in the communal
OL,13,Farea of a block of flats in Wadham
OL,14,FRoad, Bootle in Merseyside, Liverpool
OL,15,FCrown Court was told.
OL,17,FDuring the incident, on 10 February
OL,18,F2024, he suffered serious injuries to
OL,19,Fhis scalp, face and hands.
