OL,6,FAmanda Young, 49, was jailed for 20
OL,7,Fmonths after admitting being the
OL,8,Fperson in charge of a dog which caused
OL,9,Finjury while dangerously out of
OL,10,Fcontrol in a public place, on Monday
OL,11,F13 May.
OL,13,FHer son Lewis Young, 30, was given a
OL,14,Ftwo-year prison sentence after he
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty to being the owner.
OL,17,FDuring sentencing, Honorary Recorder
OL,18,Fof Liverpool Judge Andrew Menary said:
OL,19,F"The circumstances of the attack are
OL,20,Ftruly awful.
