OL,6,F"The nature of the injuries caused to
OL,7,Fthe young victim, then eight years
OL,8,Fold, were catastrophic and on any view
OL,9,Flife changing.
OL,11,F"The events of that day will no doubt
OL,12,Fhaunt the memories of everyone who
OL,13,Fwitnessed the savage and sustained
OL,14,Fattack by the dog you had decided to
OL,15,Fkeep as a pet."
OL,17,FCharlotte Kenny, prosecuting, said the
OL,18,Fyoung boy had been at the flats to
OL,19,Fplay with a friend when the attack
OL,20,Fhappened.
