OL,6,FThe court heard the dog was
OL,7,F"unrestrained" and "uncontrolled" when
OL,8,Fit started to attack the boy, having
OL,9,Fbeen allowed to wander freely around
OL,10,Fthe communal parts of the block by
OL,11,FAmanda Young.
OL,13,FMs Kenny said neighbours tried to pull
OL,14,Fthe dog from the boy, including
OL,15,FAnthony Atkinson, who grabbed the dog
OL,16,Fby its neck to try to stop the attack.
OL,18,FMr Atkinson described seeing the
OL,19,Fcanine latched on to the boy's
OL,20,Fshoulder and neck area, the court
OL,21,Fheard.
