OL,6,FOther witnesses said the dog was
OL,7,F"frothing at the mouth" and shaking
OL,8,Fthe boy's head, the court heard.
OL,10,FThe court heard Amanda Young was in
OL,11,Fcharge of the dog while her son, a
OL,12,Fdelivery driver, was at work.
OL,14,FShe later told police she had had
OL,15,Fthree or four gins, which may have
OL,16,Fbeen double measures, that afternoon.
OL,18,FThe court heard the dog was
OL,19,Fcategorised as having substantial
OL,20,Ffeatures of an XL bully-type dog.
