OL,6,FSince 1 February, it has been a
OL,7,Fcriminal offence to own an XL bully in
OL,8,FEngland and Wales without a
OL,9,Fcertificate.
OL,11,FLewis Young told police he had owned a
OL,12,Fcloth muzzle but his dog had chewed
OL,13,Fthrough it so it could not be used.
OL,15,FHe said he was "not sure" if the
OL,16,Fanimal was an XL bully and had been
OL,17,Fplanning to have it tested.
OL,19,FHe said he had owned the dog, called
OL,20,FSnoop, for two or three months after
OL,21,Fseeing him advertised on Facebook.
