OL,6,FThe court heard the victim was taken
OL,7,Fto Alder Hey Children's Hospital and
OL,8,Funderwent surgery to try to reattach
OL,9,Fhis scalp but it was unsuccessful.
OL,11,FMs Kenny said he also had a fracture
OL,12,Fto his skull consistent with the dog's
OL,13,Ftooth penetrating his scalp.
OL,15,FJudge Menary said: "This little boy
OL,16,Fhas had multiple surgeries to graft
OL,17,Fskin to his head.
