OL,6,F"He will be left, on any view, with
OL,7,Fextensive facial and scalp scarring
OL,8,Fand profound psychological scarring.
OL,9,FThe injuries are just dreadful."
OL,11,FIn a statement, the victim's mother,
OL,12,Fwho was in court with relatives, said
OL,13,Fher son had to stay in hospital for
OL,14,Fmore than two months and had not yet
OL,15,Freturned to school.
OL,17,FShe said: "He is petrified when he
OL,18,Fsees a dog and will physically grab
OL,19,Fhis dad's or my hand."
