OL,6,FDaniel Travers, defending Lewis Young,
OL,7,Fsaid he was "devastated" about the
OL,8,Fattack.
OL,10,FMr Travers said: "He (Lewis Young)
OL,11,Fwill forever regret what happened and
OL,12,Fhe knows he and his mother were
OL,13,Fcompletely to blame for what happened."
OL,15,FMartine Snowdon, defending Amanda
OL,16,FYoung, said she had mental health
OL,17,Fdifficulties and had volunteered at a
OL,18,Fcommunity centre.
OL,20,FShe said she had "genuine and profound
OL,21,Fremorse".
